Nginx RTMP Server (nrs)

This is simple bash builder for nginx with rtmp module, from UPG.GR-MEDIA-SERVER project...

-nginx ver: mainline 1.11.3
-nginx-rtmp module: git master
-Installed under /opt, in order to keep system's nginx files (if any) untouched
-modified nginx.conf with http server on 8081 port and rtmp server on (default) 1935 port
-stat page for rtmp statistics (http://yourip:8081/stat)
-Added rc script (for ubuntu and centos), called nginx-rtmp and adding it to default run-levels

USAGE: 
-clone & edit to your needs: 
  git clone https://github.com/beginho/nrs.git
  
-quick run w/o cloning UBUNTU: 
  curl -sL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/beginho/nrs/master/nginx_ubuntu.sh | sudo bash -

-quick run w/o cloning CENTOS: 
  curl -sL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/beginho/nrs/master/nginx_centos.sh | sudo bash -
  
Tested with Ubuntu 14.04 Server and Centos 6.7

